03/10/76   edit replace, edit rep

Function:  substitutes a given character string within a specified line
or range of lines.


Syntax:  edit replace /old_string/new_string/line1{ line2 ... lineN}


Arguments:
/  string delimiter.
old_string  string to be located.
new_string  string to be substituted for old_string.
linei  line number or range of lines within which substitution occurs.
